incorrectly in the outline view.

Change locale to German. 
Create a standard C++ project called NL.
Create the makefile as follows:
	all: NL.exe

	main.o: main.cpp
		g++ -c main.cpp -o main.o

	NL.exe: main.o
		g++ -O3 -o NL.exe main.o

	clean: 
		rm NL.exe main.o
main.cpp looks like:
	#include <iostream>
	using namespace std;

	int main(int argc, char **argv) {
		cout << "Hello CDT!" << endl;
	}
 	int Li脽盲(){} 

The method Li脽盲 shows up in the outline view as "Li(): int".

